P(5 \text{ before 7}) = P(5) + P(\neg 7 \neg 5, 5) + P(\neg 7 \neg 5, \neg 7 \neg 5, 5) + ....
\frac{4}{36}+\frac{26}{36}\frac{4}{36} + ...\left( \frac{26}{36} \right)^n\frac{4}{36} = \frac{1}{9} \sum \limits_{i=0}^n \left( \frac{26}{36} \right)^i = \frac{1}{9} \frac{36}{10} = \frac{2}{5}
